00:00:34,530 --> 00:00:38,720
♫ <i>Who I met? Who I met?</i> ♫

8
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:54,890
<i>[Ji Sub Lim]</i>

9
00:00:54,890 --> 00:00:57,530
<i>[Jun Taek Oh]</i>

10
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,660
♫ <i>Why are we headed there?</i> ♫

11
00:01:00,660 --> 00:01:04,970
♫ <i>What are we walking for?</i> ♫

12
